 />\nA little bit complex LOL. In short, semiotic can be understand as a relationship of encoding and decoding. A meaning of message will be addressed by ways of a suitable face in certain &quot;context&quot;.<br />\nSince the human society is builders from huge amounts of information, the combinations of these info will be generate together and form up a called &quot;cultural&quot; . We study to unfold this relationship in giving meaning (or let's say information&quot; <br />\n<br />\nIn the modern society, artists would try to challenge or quest the &quot;existing&quot; . In terms of art, they trend to distort, to destruct, to blend, to overdrive - which they are giving their own understand to a &quot;existing&quot;. Therefore, semiotic is a must for people to read postmodern art(當代藝術）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nDerrida？"},{"pid":"ac58117574c1c7ee33f0ee0b1ad083b9f1d35573","tid":397076,"uid":56498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T09:36:04.000Z","msg":"當代藝術是否活該無人鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0029c9acbec8082ee722909ee2612b509b0588f","tid":397076,"uid":43141,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:49:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當代藝術是否活該無人鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實你連當代藝術 (contemporary art) 同插圖 (illustration) 都未識分，全盤否定當代藝術，覺得整個藝術史嘅發展同今天藝術界所做嘅都係徒勞，又有咩好講呢？"},{"pid":"fde2f49470ea9269aca0af9069486e2fbd707d9c","tid":397076,"uid":54685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T11:01:28.000Z","msg":"唔識畫畫，對畫畫零興趣<br />\n淨係識跳舞<br />\n自己覺得現代舞唔易跳<br />\n唔係講技術，係講意義上好難<br />\n當代藝術絕對唔可以忽視當代舞<br />\n唔好淨係討論畫畫<br />\n<br />\n利申：乜都唔識留名學野"},{"pid":"02059dc082af944d0d27099729f0f3419f402fd0","tid":397076,"uid":56498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T11:21:13.000Z","msg":"硬要講，當個標題寫住鍾意唔鍾意個陣已經注定無野好講"},{"pid":"38fb0f8c78d65fb5100249a9cd9efa6bd860b829","tid":397076,"uid":4